	<strong>Description:</strong></p>
<p>
	Be a part of one of the fastest growing <a href="http://gamesthatgive.net">social gaming companies</a> on the planet and help drive a socially responsible revolution. We build custom branded Facebook games with a twist, our games drive donations to charity!</p>
<p>
	We are looking for a dedicated, upbeat, socially responsible minded and well-organized sales professional to join our sales team. As an integral part of the sales organization, this Inside Sales Associate is responsible for generating new leads and setting up game demos for our sales team. We are looking for team players who perform well under pressure and work well in a small team environment. Our compensation package rewards focus and hard work. Plus, there is opportunity for quick growth for those who surpass expectations.</p>
<p>
	Our current customers include such venerable brands as Best Buy, Starbucks, Dial Soap, Domino&rsquo;s, MasterCard, and Pepsi and we are growing our client base. If you have a passion for games, a strong social conscience and a desire to make a difference as part of a fast growth, high energy organization, Games That Give is the place for you.</p>
<p>
	San Francisco Bay Area residents only please.</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	<strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Effectively prospect, identify, and qualify sales leads</li>
	<li>
		Set up game demos for sales team</li>
	<li>
		Help us socialize our brand and generate buzz in the marketing community</li>
	<li>
		Build lasting relationships to drive success across industry verticals</li>
	<li>
		Leverage tools and technology to track and measure sales efforts</li>
	<li>
		Interact with leading brand managers, media planners and creative agencies.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	<strong>Minimum</strong> <strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
