	<li>
		Strong proficiency with SalesForce or similar CRM tool</li>
	<li>
		Ability to generate creative marketing solutions for brands</li>
	<li>
		Hard-working, detail-orientated individual with a strong team commitment</li>
	<li>
		Excellent phone selling and presentation skills</li>
	<li>
		Motivated, self-starter that is driven by success</li>
	<li>
		Ability to meet and exceed individual sales targets on a consistent basis</li>
	<li>
		Bachelors degree or equivalent required</li>
